<dc:title>CORE Jazz Album</dc:title>
<dc:subject>compilation jazz album CORE used as a fundraiser for the organization.</dc:subject>
<dc:description>RECORD ONE, SIDE ONE:    
Dinah Washington, &quot;The Blues Ain&#039;t Nothing But a Woman Cryin For Her Man&quot;; Cannonball Adderly with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Cannonology&quot;; Harry Belafante with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Lean on Me&quot;; Herbie Mann with Machito and his Orchestra, &quot;Carabunta&quot;; Steve Allen&#039;s Roundtable All-Stars, &quot;I Thought About You&quot;; Chris Connor and Maynard Ferguson, &quot;I Feel a Song Coming On&quot;.

RECORD ONE, SIDE TWO:
Louis Armstrong and Duke Ellington, &quot;Cotton Tail&quot;; John Coltrane Quartet, &quot;Exotica&quot;; Dizzy Gillespie, &quot;Paris Swing&quot;; Erroll Garner, &quot;Love for Sale&quot;; Woody Herman Sextet with Nat Adderley, &quot;Lullaby of Birdland&quot;; Charlie Parker &amp; Miles Davis, &quot;Klactoveededstene&quot;

RECORD TWO, SIDE ONE:
